tun-route.c - program to create the NON-PERSISTENT tun device
tun-setup.sh - setup to route packets via the tun device created

Steps as user root:
1) Run ./a.out  on one terminal
2) Run ./tun-setup.sh on the other termina
3) Then start the ipsec tunnel
4) Capture packets using tcpdump on the tun0 device  

The sample trace is included in this folder. 
